{"tid":1864493,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】本港第21宗確診 - 曾去東京","createTime":"2020-02-05T15:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T01:15:34.000Z","uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0c411283bd5177ccb972fcd3337fc293a2a4c4","tid":1864493,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"第21宗個案：56歲男性 確診日期：2月5日 備注：於深圳工作<br />\n14日內去過內地<br />\n<br />\n居住青衣灝景灣一座<br />\n<br />\n28/1-1/2到過東京，乘坐香港快運UO651返港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPjGy6z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPjGy6z.jpg&h=1968690d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://l.hkott.hk/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=17056&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fl.hkott.hk%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D17056%26ct%3D1&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=86c5bf78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://l.hkott.hk/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=17056&amp;ct=1</a>"},{"pid":"e9289863fe17058416404a8b496ae8be0240d990","tid":1864493,"uid":177168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDPGeQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDPGeQ.png&h=f227900c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家疫情有爆發跡象，十萬火急！藍田女手足全家確診武漢肺炎，請大家幫手簽下面的聯署：<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手行多步宣傳下比你ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同身邊既朋友。<br />\n另外大家亦可以透過聯署同twitter自行遊說美方人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呼籲研發出肺炎解藥的美國藥廠供貨香港救手足救香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=7a4ade37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n給予港府壓力封閉所有連接中國大陸的口岸<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fexert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=a19514d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國CDC、軍方醫療船派遣人員到香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=6c63d1f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署要求世衛主席辭職<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Funited-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=13afa120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general</a><br />\n<br />\n美孚手足被爆頭要推上 twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Domo96954201/status/1223987271344390144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDomo96954201%2Fstatus%2F1223987271344390144&d=SLV